 <h2 className="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Benefits of Assuming a Mortgage in Fountain</h2>
 <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
 <div className="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
 <h3 className="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">Lower Interest Rates</h3>
 <p className="text-gray-700">
 Lock in rates as low as {minRate}%, significantly below current market rates of 6.5% or higher. This can save you hundreds of dollars every month.
 </p>
