 <div className="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
 <h3 className="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">Faster Closing</h3>
 <p className="text-gray-700">
 Skip traditional lender underwriting. Assuming a mortgage typically closes in 2-3 weeks instead of 30-45 days, getting you into your home sooner.
 </p>
 </div>
 <div className="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
 <h3 className="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">Lower Closing Costs</h3>
