 Many assumable loans in Fountain are FHA or VA loans, offering flexibility for military families and first-time homebuyers.
 </p>
 </div>
 <div className="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
 <h3 className="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">Predictable Payments</h3>
 <p className="text-gray-700">
 Assuming a fixed-rate mortgage means your payment never changes, providing stability and budget certainty for years to come.
 </p>
 </div>
 <div className="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
 <h3 className="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-3">Less Competition</h3>
